Sentencas: This paper describes a manometric method for the determination of chemical diffusion coefficients from gas/solid equilibration kinetics for electrode materials of the type (La,Sr)(Mn,Fe,Co)O-3.
Titulo: A manometric method for the determination of chemical diffusion in perovskite-type cathode materials of the solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The equilibration kinetics was monitored by measurements of the p(O-2) changes during a reaction between oxygen and the electrode material involving both oxidation and reduction experiments in the temperature range 773-1123 K. Activation energy of the chemical diffusion measurements at different temperatures was determined during both oxidation and reduction experiments.
Titulo: A manometric method for the determination of chemical diffusion in perovskite-type cathode materials of the solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The chemical diffusion coefficients measured by the present manometric method on La0.8Sr0.2 MnO3-delta have been compared with those reported in the literature.
Titulo: A manometric method for the determination of chemical diffusion in perovskite-type cathode materials of the solid oxide fuel cell
